data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Back on the Market!!! Buyers financing fell through. IMMACULATE HOME completely renovated and move-in ready.  This perfectly designed 2 Bedroom, 2 bath open split plan home has an oversized 1 Car Garage, a large front patio courtyard at the entrance, and multiple living areas that can be used to your liking.  The kitchen has all new modern white cabinets with a built-in wine rack, drawers, beautiful countertops, stainless steel appliances, faucet, and hardware.  The bathrooms also have NEW cabinets, countertops, sleek subway wall tiles, rectangular sinks, framed mirrors, faucets & fixtures.  The home features energy efficient exterior windows, cedar closets throughout, tile flooring (NO CARPET), water softener, NEWER water heater (2017) and AC (2021), and rain gutters.  The 2 sliding glass doors off the living and family rooms lead you to an enclosed sunroom with lots of windows and wood plank ceiling perfect for entertaining and enjoying the home from the inside out.  This home is in the desirable Colonial Hills community with NO HOA, NO CDD FEEs, and Flood Insurance is NOT required. The home is conveniently located near parks, hospital, shopping, restaurants, beaches, just minutes to US 19 and Highway 54.  This home is a must see.  Schedule your tour today!
